						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1305 (1383 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>In Sanskrit verse written in Grantha. Registers a gift of land by <hi rend="bold">Muddarasa</hi> the minister of <hi rend="bold">Virūpāksha,</hi> for rearing a flower-garden for supply of garlands to the god, The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1305</hi> (in chronogram <hi rend="bold">mānaślāghyē</hi>), <hi rend="bold">Kārttika, paurṇamī, Tuesday, Kṛittikā</hi> correspond regularly to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1383, November 10, Tuesday, ·78; ·58.</hi></p>						

